result.name: Malty

reviews.text: Nice place but staff so ignorant and detached it's quite bizarre. They hide at the end of the bar trying desperately to avoid any customer contact at all, and when contact is unavoidable they're dogmatic and rude, almost confrontational or truculent.  Why the heck did these girls choose to work in the hospitality industry when they'd be much more suited to working at the DMV, IRS or Death Star?
Very relaxed atmosphere with sport on the big screen, cold beers and a huge selection of malt whiskeys. Free snacks, and food is great.
Excellent collection of single malt whiskys
I mean, I think it's nice! The staff are sweet, drinks come kinda quickly, and it's a nice enough environment. Channels are a bit boring, but I don't think that's the bar's fault! 5 outta 5!
Excellent planned to have a quick drink before or after dinner in tai hang area. Friendly staff.
